data.description: This stunning 2-story brick home was a Jeff Benton Model Home!  This home offers 5 bedrooms & 5 baths, adorned with beautiful landscaping and a large backyard featuring a pergola & deck.The Grand Foyer welcomes you & leads to a formal dining room great for entertaining. The kitchen boasts a large island and granite countertops, blending style and functionality seamlessly. A luxurious soaking tub off the spacious owner's retreat. Entertainment is elevated with a surround sound speaker system, and practicality is ensured with a whole house surge protector. The home is wired with electric car chargers, catering to eco-conscious individuals. This home harmonizes luxury & modern amenities.
